SELECT A.HO_CODE1 HO_CODE , A.BUNHO BUNHO , A.SUNAME SUNAME , A.PKINP1001 PKINP1001 , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(:f_date,A.BIRTH,'')||'/'||A.SEX AGE_SEX --, NVL(A.SIL_IPWON_DATE,NVL(A.CHT_IPWON_DATE, A.IPWON_DATE)) IPWON_DATE , A.IPWON_DATE IPWON_DATE , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD')) DOCTOR_NAME , A.CYCLE_ORDER_GROUP FROM VW_OCS_INP1001_01 A , BAS0250 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HO_DONG1 = :f_ho_dong AND A.IPWON_DATE <= TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND A.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HO_DONG = A.HO_DONG1 AND B.HO_CODE = A.HO_CODE1 AND ((NVL(:f_a, 'N') = 'Y' and B.TEAM = 'A') OR (NVL(:f_b, 'N') = 'Y' and B.TEAM = 'B') OR (NVL(:f_c, 'N') = 'Y' and B.TEAM = 'C') OR (NVL(:f_d, 'N') = 'Y' and B.TEAM = 'D') OR (NVL(:f_a, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(:f_b, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(:f_c, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(:f_d, 'N') = 'N' ) )
ORDER BY B.HO_SORT, A.BED_NO

data.name: grdNUR1122.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT B.BUNHO, B.FKINP1001, A.YMD, A.HANGMOG_CODE, DECODE (:f_prevqryflag, 'Y', '', A.HANGMOG_VALUE1) HANGMOG_VALUE1, DECODE (:f_prevqryflag, 'Y', '', A.HANGMOG_VALUE2) HANGMOG_VALUE2, DECODE (:f_prevqryflag, 'Y', '', A.HANGMOG_VALUE3) HANGMOG_VALUE3, B.HANGMOG_NAME, C.END_YN FROM NUR1122 A , (SELECT ROWNUM ROW_NUM, Y.HANGMOG_NAME, Y.HOSP_CODE, Y.FKINP1001, Y.BUNHO FROM (SELECT Z.HANGMOG_NAME, Z.HOSP_CODE, Z.FKINP1001, Z.BUNHO FROM NUR1122 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND Z.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND Z.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001 AND Z.YMD BETWEEN TO_DATE(:f_ymd, 'YYYY/MM/DD')-6 AND TO_DATE(:f_ymd, 'YYYY/MM/DD') GROUP BY Z.HANGMOG_NAME, Z.HOSP_CODE, Z.FKINP1001, Z.BUNHO HAVING NOT (COUNT(Z.HANGMOG_VALUE1) = 0 AND COUNT(Z.HANGMOG_VALUE2) = 0 AND COUNT(Z.HANGMOG_VALUE3) = 0) ORDER BY 1 ) Y) B , (SELECT DISTINCT X.HOSP_CODE, X.FKINP1001, X.HANGMOG_NAME, 'Y' END_YN FROM NUR1122 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND X.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND X.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001 AND '//' IN (X.HANGMOG_VALUE1, X.HANGMOG_VALUE2, X.HANGMOG_VALUE3) AND X.YMD BETWEEN TO_DATE(:f_ymd, 'YYYY/MM/DD')-6 AND TO_DATE(:f_ymd, 'YYYY/MM/DD')) C WHERE A.HOSP_CODE (+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.FKINP1001 (+)= B.FKINP1001 AND A.YMD (+) = TO_DATE (:f_ymd, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND A.HANGMOG_NAME (+) = B.HANGMOG_NAME AND C.HOSP_CODE (+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.FKINP1001(+) = B.FKINP1001 AND C.HANGMOG_NAME(+) = B.HANGMOG_NAME ORDER BY B.ROW_NUM

data.value: SELECT MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'SYO' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) SYO , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'AS' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) DUNG_SYO , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'AX' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) DUNG_CNT , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'UT' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) URINE_QUANTITY , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'UX' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) URINE_CNT , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'HEIGHT' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) HEIGHT , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WEIGHT' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) WEIGHT , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'CARE' , HANGMOG_VALUE, '')) CARE , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WRITER', DECODE(A.HANGMOG_SEQ, 1, HANGMOG_VALUE, ''))) WRITER_ID_1 , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WRITER', DECODE(A.HANGMOG_SEQ, 1, FN_ADM_LOAD_USER_NAME(HANGMOG_VALUE), ''))) WRITER_NM_1 , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WRITER', DECODE(A.HANGMOG_SEQ, 2, HANGMOG_VALUE, ''))) WRITER_ID_2 , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WRITER', DECODE(A.HANGMOG_SEQ, 2, FN_ADM_LOAD_USER_NAME(HANGMOG_VALUE), ''))) WRITER_NM_2 , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WRITER', DECODE(A.HANGMOG_SEQ, 3, HANGMOG_VALUE, ''))) WRITER_ID_3 , MIN(DECODE(A.HANGMOG_GUBUN, 'WRITER', DECODE(A.HANGMOG_SEQ, 3, FN_ADM_LOAD_USER_NAME(HANGMOG_VALUE), ''))) WRITER_NM_3 FROM (SELECT A.BUNHO BUNHO , A.FKINP1001 FKINP1001 , A.YMD YMD , A.HANGMOG_GUBUN HANGMOG_GUBUN , TO_CHAR(A.HANGMOG_SEQ) HANGMOG_SEQ , A.HANGMOG_VALUE HANGMOG_VALUE FROM NUR7002 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.YMD = :f_ymd AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001 UNION SELECT B.BUNHO BUNHO , B.FKINP1001 FKINP1001 , B.YMD YMD , B.IO_TYPE HANGMOG_GUBUN , '1' HANGMOG_SEQ , TO_CHAR(B.IO_VALUE) HANGMOG_VALUE FROM NUR1022 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.YMD = :f_ymd AND B.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001) A
